ocl:
context Address
inv: self.city <> null implies self.country <> null

context AccountTransaction
inv: self.type.size() >= 2 implies self.type.substring(1, 2) = 'value'

context CreditCard
inv: self.cardTransactions->size() >= 5 implies self.cardTransactions->asSequence()->at(5).merchant <> null

context Account
inv: self.accountNo.size() >= 10 implies self.accountNo.substring(1, 10) = 'value'

context Account
inv: self.accountNo.size() >= 5 implies self.accountNo.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context Account
inv: self.balance >= 18 and self.balance <= 60

context Customer
inv: self.cards->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.isActive <> y.isActive)

context Account
inv: self.accountNo <> '' and self.accountNo.size() > 0

context Branch
inv: self.customers->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.fullName <> y.fullName)

context Bank
inv: self.name <> '' and self.name.size() > 0

context Branch
inv: self.branchCode.size() >= 6 implies self.branchCode.substring(1, 6) = 'value'

context Bank
inv: self.branches->notEmpty() implies self.branches->sortedBy(x | x.city)->first().city <= self.branches->sortedBy(x | x.city)->last().city

context CreditCard
inv: self.limit >= 37 and self.limit <= 85

context Employee
inv: not(self.employeeId <> null and self.name <> null)

context Bank
inv: (self.branches->size() >= 1 and self.branches->size() <= 1) and (self.branches->size() < 1)

context Address
inv: not((self.country <> null and self.postalCode = null) or (self.country = null and self.postalCode <> null))

context Customer
inv: (self.cards->size() >= 2 implies self.cards->asSequence()->at(2).limit <> null) and (self.cards->size() < 2)

context Customer
inv: (self.cards->notEmpty() implies self.cards->sortedBy(x | x.cardNo)->first().cardNo <= self.cards->sortedBy(x | x.cardNo)->last().cardNo) and (self.cards->isEmpty())

context Branch
inv: (self.customers->notEmpty() implies self.customers->last().email <> null) and (self.customers->isEmpty())

context Account
inv: not(self.accountNo.size() >= 5 implies self.accountNo.substring(1, 5) = 'value')

context Customer
inv: (self.accounts->notEmpty() implies self.accounts->first().balance <> null) and (self.accounts->isEmpty())

context Branch
inv: not(self.branchCode <> null implies self.city <> null)
